'''Roast gornt''' was a [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] dish. It consisted of chunks of roasted [[Gornt/Legends|gornt]] meat, which had a tough texture, and was covered in a lumpy brownish gravy. It was served at [[Car'ulorn's Kavsrach]], although Twi'leks considered it to be a tourist dish.

